      <title>罗森伯格称加拿大应避免打不赢的贸易战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/david-rosenberg-says-canada-should-avoid-a-trade-war-it-can-t-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家戴维·罗森伯格表示，如果加拿大对特朗普总统的潜在关税采取报复措施，贸易战过后，加拿大所受的伤害将比美国严重得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/david-rosenberg-says-canada-should-avoid-a-trade-war-it-can-t-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 14:45:44 GMT</pubDate>
